{"tid":161311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真球例討論) 蘇狗個球十二碼判得岩唔岩","createTime":"2017-03-18T12:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T11:27:30.000Z","uid":72652,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f25d8c98c4ec200fd138ba98f792ea18643a104f","tid":161311,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"盲反/疤迷可以上一頁<br />\n<br />\n我個人意見：<br />\n<br />\n一個前鋒準備單對單面對球門<br />\n已經拎哂身位<br />\n後衛係無機會掂到個波之下<br />\n用手影響對手攻門+隻腳click到人地隻腳<br />\n即使未必導致對方跌倒<br />\n但由於你係完全無機會掂到波<br />\n技術上就係從後攔截<br />\n一定可以判<br />\n<br />\n當然蘇9專登放軟個身跌<br />\n你可以插佢無體育精神唔繼續攻門<br />\n但佢只係放大個動作比球證睇<br />\n你可以話佢「演技好」<br />\n但唔會係無中生有的「插水」<br />\n<br />\n同樣「從後輕微hi倒影響攻門」的例子<br />\n可以參考2005歐聯利記追平a米3比3個球<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/x2R4J_mfn5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx2R4J_mfn5I&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f7f9a225\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/x2R4J_mfn5I</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/4OTOvbgFiYI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4OTOvbgFiYI&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5507dd13\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/4OTOvbgFiYI</a><br />\n留意馬昆奴斯右腳click到蘇9右腳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/2MGdlo5Y0XQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2MGdlo5Y0XQ&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c571cf73\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/2MGdlo5Y0XQ</a><br />\n睇埋wide shot<br />\n馬昆奴斯從後直接「挨」埋影響對手平衡<br />\n<br />\n都係個句<br />\n五五波就實冇問題<br />\n單刀真係吹緊<br />\n怪就怪自己多手<br />\n<br />\n其實連登有幾多人真係識少少球例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e924894f246977d2880fa885fb20b4aa305456","tid":161311,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedafa50bcc5b7ef2c3dcefe25a24013940952fb","tid":161311,"uid":17842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做乜鳩"},{"pid":"bc47dd5623d5a5771f07cb5923331386c2c1b7fe","tid":161311,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理性討論呀撚樣<br />\n而家無分邊撚個做呀<br />\n下下搬蝗疤出嚟仲討論乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"32ff3855ff1e5668869001dea40a27b9ad511637","tid":161311,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fb65f8c68b886788b96073f58b23406f9eadbf","tid":161311,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理性討論呀撚樣<br />\n而家無分邊撚個做呀<br />\n下下搬蝗疤出嚟仲討論乜撚嘢</blockquote><br />\n樓主都有叫巴迷出返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔係預設立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd2d545582c17374075bdb583a6864b8c2995ef","tid":161311,"uid":65535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"利申左巴狗先<br />\n完全同意樓主嘅論點<br />\n蘇狗跌係因為被侵犯，果下完全構成犯規，因為蘇狗係有明顯優勢可以攞到個波，馬昆奴斯點樣輕微掂到蘇狗都會影響到蘇狗明顯構成入球嘅優勢，當然蘇狗果下表演係好冇體育精神，但係果個時候博12碼係更有可能入波，身為專業球員應該以球隊利益為先，加上球隊落後下又冇乜時間剩，跌得跨張博12碼係最合理嘅判斷，你可以屌蘇狗表演，但係佢冇插水，喱下都唔係黑哨"},{"pid":"1704878fc57320801c82b3f73a209a4c0ba5d624","tid":161311,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"其實都吹得啱"},{"pid":"eb70757b8f0bcab201654a4533b72efefa5aea50","tid":161311,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理性討論呀撚樣<br />\n而家無分邊撚個做呀<br />\n下下搬蝗疤出嚟仲討論乜撚嘢</blockquote><br />\n樓主都有叫巴迷出返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔係預設立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你走吧啦<br />\n邊忽有話蘇9熱血<br />\n佢都插左張黃牌返黎仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2a67cdba40a374d54e455e22d90544156f78e3","tid":161311,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿朗做 &gt;插水狗<br />\n蘇狗做 &gt;為球隊爭取利益+熱血反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理性討論呀撚樣<br />\n而家無分邊撚個做呀<br />\n下下搬蝗疤出嚟仲討論乜撚嘢</blockquote><br />\n樓主都有叫巴迷出返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔係預設立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你走吧啦<br />\n邊忽有話蘇9熱血<br />\n佢都插左張黃牌返黎仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又冇話你有話蘇9熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nme引用近排巴迷意見黎延伸討論姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}